uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.content

Interface UIProvider


  • public interface UIProvider
    An interface for objects that can produce a UIGenerator to add themselves to a ContentBuilder. This serves the same purpose as the UIGenerator interface but is better suited to cases where the content logic is added by composition.

    spb
